The '''Mont Nlonako Wildlife Reserve''' is a [[Nature reserve|wildlife reserve]] and a proposed [[protected area]] ([[World Database on Protected Areas|WDPA]] ID: 308631) in the [[Littoral Region, Cameroon|Littoral Region]] of [[Cameroon]].  This nature reserve covers an area of approximately {{Convert|641.24|km²|sqmi}}, on the south-east side of the city of [[Nkongsamba]], starting from Mont Nlonako.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wdpa.org/siteSheet.aspx?sitecode=308631 |title=Mont Nlonako Wildlife Reserve |publisher=protectedplanet.net }}</ref>

