{{Infobox diocese |jurisdiction = Diocese |name = Tanjung Selor |latin = Dioecesis Tanjungselorensis |local = Keuskupan Tanjung Selor |country = [[Indonesia]] |metropolitan = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Samarinda|Samarinda]] |province = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Samarinda|Samarinda]] |rite = [[Latin Rite]] |cathedral = Cathedral of the Assumption in [[Tanjung Selor]] |cocathedral = |area_km2 = 96,630 |population = 482,000 |population_as_of = 2004 |catholics = 40,772 |catholics_percent= 8.5 |pope = {{Incumbent pope}} |bishop = [[Mgr Paulinus Yan Olla]], [[Missionaries of the Holy Family|M.S.F.]] |metro_archbishop = [[Justinus Harjosusanto]], [[Missionaries of the Holy Family|M.S.F.]] |coadjutor = |auxiliary_bishops= }}
The '''Roman Catholic Diocese of Tanjung Selor''' ({{lang-la| Tanjungseloren(sis)}}) is a [[diocese]] located in the city of [[Tanjung Selor]] in the [[Ecclesiastical province]] of [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Samarinda|Samarinda]] in Indonesia.
==History== * January 9, 2002: Established as the Diocese of Tanjung Selor from the Diocese of Samarinda
==Leadership== * [[Bishop]]s of Tanjung Selor (Roman rite) ** Bishop Justinus Tarmana Harjosusanto, [[Missionaries of the Holy Family|M.S.F.]] (January 9, 2002 – February 16, 2015) ** Bishop Paulinus Yan Olla, [[Missionaries of the Holy Family|M.S.F.]] (May 5,2018 - present)
==References== * [http://www.gcatholic.org/dioceses/diocese/tanj2.htm GCatholic.org] * [http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dtase.html Catholic Hierarchy]
