'''Volta Star FM''' is a public radio station in [[Ho, Ghana|Ho]], the capital town of the [[Volta Region]] of [[Ghana]].<ref name=Radio>{{cite web|title=Radio|url=http://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/communication/radio.php|publisher=www.ghanaweb.com|accessdate=10 March 2012}}</ref> The station is owned and run by the state broadcaster - the [[Ghana Broadcasting Corporation]].<ref name=GBC>{{cite web|title=Ghana Broadcasting Cooperation|url=http://www.gbcghana.com/|publisher=www.gbcghana.com|accessdate=10 March 2012}}</ref><ref name=RW>{{cite web|title=Radio Station World|url=http://radiostationworld.com/locations/ghana/Radio.asp|publisher=www.radiostationworld.com|accessdate=10 March 2012}}</ref>
